[Name] Perl-Pod-Simple
[Summary] Perl framework for parsing files in Pod markup language
[Description] Pod::Simple is a Perl library for parsing text in the
Pod ("plain old documentation") markup language that is typically used
for writing documentation for Perl and for Perl modules
